<https://tomascp-sudo.github.io/medicalDeviceOntology/1.0/ontology.owl> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ontology about medical devices, their classification, incidents, risks and corrective actions." .
<https://tomascp-sudo.github.io/medicalDeviceOntology/1.0/ontology.owl> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Medical Devices Classification and Safety Ontology"@en .
<https://tomascp-sudo.github.io/medicalDeviceOntology/1.0/ontology.owl> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "Version 1.0" .
<https://tomascp-sudo.github.io/medicalDeviceOntology/1.0/ontology.owl> <https://tomascp-sudo.github.io/medical-device-ontology/ontology.owl#schma:includedInDataCatalog> "This ontology is about medical devices, their classification, and the safety mechanisms associated with their use, including incidents and corrective actions." .
<https://tomascp-sudo.github.io/medicalDeviceOntology/1.0/ontology.owl> <https://tomascp-sudo.github.io/medical-device-ontology/ontology.owl#vann:preferredNamespacePrefix> "EUDAMED" .
<https://tomascp-sudo.github.io/medicalDeviceOntology/1.0/ontology.owl> <https://tomascp-sudo.github.io/medicalDeviceOntology/1.0/ontology.owl#logo> "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Small_logo_UOC.svg/3840px-Small_logo_UOC.svg.png" .
